divs: Sighting DetailsI was in Amsterdam, just taking a photo of the city. At the time , I didn't see anything in the sky. At about 5 seconds later, I took another photo at the same place. I checked both photos and realised that on one photo was a sphere object and on the other photo was nothing. The object disappeard immediately. I was amazed by this but very happy.

Summary: A sphere object in the sky.
